tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: The patient shows leukocytosis, mild anemia (low erythrocytes and hemoglobin), and a markedly elevated platelet distribution width. These findings may indicate an ongoing inflammatory or infectious process and possible bone marrow response. Correlation with clinical context and further evaluation for infection, inflammation, or hematologic disorders is recommended.
